  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: When sending small ETH amount in one-to-one or group chat message layout is broken\r\n\r\nAndroid:\r\n<img width=\"516\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-03-02 at 10 35 02 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29711298/36920855-c7c901fa-1e6a-11e8-8bd5-4fa9851b8c66.png\">\r\n\r\niOS:\r\n<img width=\"516\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-03-02 at 10 35 02 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29711298/36920898-ec81ec78-1e6a-11e8-98cc-36a2e6b322c2.jpeg\">\r\n\r\n \r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nSmall amount should be rounded in the send funds message\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nBroken layout of the send funds message for both recipient and sender\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create new or sign in to existing account\r\n- Open one-to-one or group chat\r\n- Send 0.0000000001 ETH from a chat\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nStatus version: 0.9.10-740-gba056bee+, 0.9.11d740 (nightly build from 02.03)\r\nOperating System:\r\nOnePlus 5, Android 8.0.0\r\niPhone 8+, iOS 11.1.1\r\n",
